OL,3,CHoliday firm reports spike in demand
OL,4,Cfor long-haul trips
OL,6,FA holiday company has reported demand
OL,7,Ffor summer trips to faraway
OL,8,Fdestinations is growing faster than
OL,9,Ffor short-haul breaks.
OL,11,FThomas Cook said this is due to
OL,12,Ffamilies being "more adventurous" in
OL,13,Fthe wake of coronavirus travel
OL,14,Frestrictions being lifted around the
OL,15,Fworld.
