OL,3,CHoliday firm reports spike in demand
OL,4,Cfor long-haul trips
OL,6,FIts overall number of bookings for
OL,7,Flong-haul holidays in July and August
OL,8,Fis two-and-a-half times higher than at
OL,9,Fthe same point last year, whereas the
OL,10,Fincrease for trips to all locations is
OL,11,Fjust 17%.
OL,13,FSales of holidays on Mauritius, an
OL,14,Fisland in the Indian Ocean, have risen
OL,15,Fthree-fold to exceed more established
OL,16,Fsummer hotspots closer to home such as
OL,17,FGreece's Mykonos and Kefalonia,
OL,18,FPortugal's Madeira and Italy's
OL,19,FSardinia.
