OL,3,CHoliday firm reports spike in demand
OL,4,Cfor long-haul trips
OL,6,FTwo-thirds of Mauritius bookings are
OL,7,Ffor family breaks, compared with
OL,8,Faround half to Greece.
OL,10,FThe US remains Thomas Cook's number
OL,11,Fone long-distance summer destination
OL,12,Fwith a 60% year-on-year rise in
OL,13,Fdemand, followed by Mexico and
OL,14,FMauritius.
OL,16,FThomas Cook head of product Emma King
OL,17,Fsaid: "Now the shadow of Covid is long
OL,18,Fbehind us, families are becoming more
OL,19,Fadventurous with their summer holiday
OL,20,Fplans and more people are heading
OL,21,Ffurther afield.
