OL,3,CHoliday firm reports spike in demand
OL,4,Cfor long-haul trips
OL,6,F"Florida has always been a popular
OL,7,Ffamily summer holiday choice but now
OL,8,FMexico is rivalling it ` and this
OL,9,Fyear, Mauritius has leapt in
OL,10,Fpopularity.
OL,12,F"The summers in Mauritius are cooler
OL,13,Fthan you will see on the Med but still
OL,14,Faround 25C so can be better for
OL,15,Ffamilies who prefer to be more active
OL,16,Fduring the day or who want to explore
OL,17,Fa different part of the world."
