OL,3,CHoliday firm reports spike in demand
OL,4,Cfor long-haul trips
OL,6,FAir Mauritius launched daily flights
OL,7,Fbetween Gatwick airport and the island
OL,8,Fnation in October 2023, while other UK
OL,9,Fairports offer routes via the Middle
OL,10,FEast.
OL,12,FThe UK lifted its last remaining
OL,13,Fcoronavirus travel restrictions in
OL,14,FMarch 2022.
OL,16,FBut some parts of the world,
OL,17,Fparticularly in Asia, kept rules in
OL,18,Fplace until late 2023, meaning many UK
OL,19,Fholidaymakers avoided long-haul trips
OL,20,Flast year.
