OL,3,CHoliday firm reports spike in demand
OL,4,Cfor long-haul trips
OL,6,FA spokesperson for luxury holiday
OL,7,Fcompany Kuoni reported that Mauritius
OL,8,Fand Thailand are "proving extremely
OL,9,Fpopular" due to offering good value
OL,10,Ffor money, high quality hotels and
OL,11,Fresorts, and the opportunity to enjoy
OL,12,F"rich cultural experiences".
OL,14,FThree out of four of its Thailand
OL,15,Fbookings are for holidays involving
OL,16,Fmultiple locations, demonstrating the
OL,17,Fdemand for "experimental and diverse
OL,18,Ftravel experiences", she added.
