OL,3,CHoliday firm reports spike in demand
OL,4,Cfor long-haul trips
OL,6,FJulia Lo Bue-Said, chief executive of
OL,7,FAdvantage Travel Partnership, a
OL,8,Fnetwork of independent travel agents,
OL,9,Fsaid the industry is seeing strong
OL,10,Fdemand, particularly from families
OL,11,Fbooking trips before schools return.
OL,13,FShe added: "In many cases long-haul
OL,14,Ftravel can offer better value for
OL,15,Fmoney compared with a holiday to the
OL,16,FMed.
